<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 14:06:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>自杀式无人机和人工智能系统：以加沙为试验场，以色列国防初创企业蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/suicide-drones-and-ai-with-gaza-as-testing-ground-israeli-defense-startups-flourish/0000018c-cf39-ddba-abad-cfb9a3ee0000</link><description>严格的监管和主要国防公司的主导地位意味着以色列每年很少有小型国防初创公司成立。他们正在地缘政治紧张局势、军事预算增加和加沙战争中寻找新机遇</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/suicide-drones-and-ai-with-gaza-as-testing-ground-israeli-defense-startups-flourish/0000018c-cf39-ddba-abad-cfb9a3ee0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么黎巴嫩无法承受真主党和以色列之间的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/why-lebanon-cant-afford-a-war-between-hezbollah-and-israel/0000018c-cf7f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa45f0000</link><description>黎巴嫩的经济因腐败和无能而受到重创，但最终趋于稳定，游客甚至开始回归。一场全面的战争将对黎巴嫩造成致命打击</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:37:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/why-lebanon-cant-afford-a-war-between-hezbollah-and-israel/0000018c-cf7f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa45f0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯杀害歌手后，这首歌在以色列大受欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-song-became-a-big-hit-in-israel-after-hamas-killed-its-vocalist/0000018c-cf14-ddba-abad-cfb5db960000</link><description>“很遗憾我没有在她还活着的时候发行这首歌”：10 月 7 日，Ben Ronen 和 Tamar Samet 在 Nova 音乐节上，女歌手被哈马斯恐怖分子杀害后，这首精致而忧郁的歌曲获得了认可</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-song-became-a-big-hit-in-israel-after-hamas-killed-its-vocalist/0000018c-cf14-ddba-abad-cfb5db960000</guid></item><item><title>所有人的目光都集中在纳斯鲁拉身上，真主党领袖准备解决以色列杀害哈马斯官员的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/all-eyes-on-nasrallah-as-hezbollah-chief-set-to-address-israel-attributed-killing/0000018c-cf20-d4e1-ad8f-ffb18dae0000</link><description>真主党周二表示，阿鲁里在贝鲁特被杀——普遍认为是以色列所为——不会不予答复。然而，一些人认为报复不会立即发生</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 12:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/all-eyes-on-nasrallah-as-hezbollah-chief-set-to-address-israel-attributed-killing/0000018c-cf20-d4e1-ad8f-ffb18dae0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列也是我们的国家”：阿拉伯少数民族在加沙作战，同时面临国内不平等</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-our-country-too-the-arab-minority-serving-in-gaza-while-facing-inequality/0000018c-cb4c-d6c4-ab8d-ebfc204b0000</link><description>本周，自战争开始以来，第七名德鲁兹以色列国防军士兵在加沙被杀。在以色列最大的德鲁兹城镇达利亚特卡梅尔，当地人认同以色列，同时谴责其歧视性法律</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:44:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-our-country-too-the-arab-minority-serving-in-gaza-while-facing-inequality/0000018c-cb4c-d6c4-ab8d-ebfc204b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人被杀并不影响以色列在加沙的战争——但肯定会影响第二天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/al-arouri-killing-does-not-affect-the-war-in-gaza-but-certainly-the-day-after/0000018c-ce82-ddba-abad-cea30c3d0000</link><description>虽然在贝鲁特杀害哈马斯高级领导人是一次行动上的成功，但它对以色列加沙战争的影响却微乎其微。然而，它有可能加速哈马斯和法塔赫之间的和解，维护哈马斯的地位，并且更重要的是，保证其领导人的生存</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/al-arouri-killing-does-not-affect-the-war-in-gaza-but-certainly-the-day-after/0000018c-ce82-ddba-abad-cea30c3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议员表示，每个人都清楚加沙人必须被摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/its-clear-to-everyone-gazans-must-be-destroyed-israeli-lawmaker-says/0000018c-ce57-ddba-abad-cef736e40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡党议员表示，“摧毁”加沙地带公民的广泛呼声证明右翼“一直”都是正确的</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:12:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/its-clear-to-everyone-gazans-must-be-destroyed-israeli-lawmaker-says/0000018c-ce57-ddba-abad-cef736e40000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯将在杀害其高级官员后对以色列进行反击。真主党也会报复吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/will-the-killing-of-hamas-leader-in-lebanon-lead-to-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-cc0f-dc35-adee-cc4f27010000</link><description>尽管真主党的纳斯鲁拉过去曾威胁要对以色列在黎巴嫩的行动进行报复，但他的行动升级也会限制他的回旋余地</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 04:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/will-the-killing-of-hamas-leader-in-lebanon-lead-to-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-cc0f-dc35-adee-cc4f27010000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗：苏莱马尼坟墓附近的“恐怖袭击”造成70人死亡；纳斯鲁拉将解决贝鲁特罢工问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-live/hezbollah-threatens-israel-after-top-hamas-official-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut/0000018c-ccf4-d266-a9bf-edf645660000</link><description>伊朗官方媒体报道，在被杀将军逝世周年纪念日，在他的坟墓附近发生爆炸，造成数十人死亡和受伤 ■ 报道显示，人质谈判在杀戮期间停止 ■ 巴勒斯坦人呼吁约旦河西岸与以色列国防军士兵对抗 ■ 真主党称萨利赫·阿鲁里被杀“赢得了胜利” “不要置之不理” ■ 自10 月7 日以来，以色列至少有1,300 名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 22,313 人死亡、57,296 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 03:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-live/hezbollah-threatens-israel-after-top-hamas-official-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut/0000018c-ccf4-d266-a9bf-edf645660000</guid></item><item><title>实际上，为什么不将定居者转移出以色列呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/actually-why-not-transfer-settlers-out-of-israel/0000018c-cbc4-dc35-adee-cbc6884a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 01:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/actually-why-not-transfer-settlers-out-of-israel/0000018c-cbc4-dc35-adee-cbc6884a0000</guid></item><item><title>阿巴斯希望美国给予他在加沙的地位并让以色列加入。但可以吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/abbas-expects-the-u-s-to-give-him-authority-in-gaza-but-can-it/0000018c-cbbf-ddba-abad-cbbf79fe0000</link><description>虽然以色列避免讨论战后第二天，但埃及已准备好与巴勒斯坦权力机构合作，并希望能够帮助防止加沙人大规模移民</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:24:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/abbas-expects-the-u-s-to-give-him-authority-in-gaza-but-can-it/0000018c-cbbf-ddba-abad-cbbf79fe0000</guid></item><item><title>美国呼吁极右翼以色列部长主张将巴勒斯坦人撤出加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-calls-out-israeli-ministers-for-advocating-transfer-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cbec-d4e1-ad8f-fffd3ad60000</link><description>这份声明是美国罕见地不及时批评以色列，更罕见的是它明确指名道姓地点名斯莫特里奇和本格维尔。反过来，他们都拒绝了美国的声明，再次强调他们所谓的“自愿移民”的必要性</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-calls-out-israeli-ministers-for-advocating-transfer-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cbec-d4e1-ad8f-fffd3ad60000</guid></item><item><title>与辛瓦尔协调，与真主党联系在一起：谁是哈马斯最高领导人萨利赫·阿鲁里？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/coordinated-with-sinwar-tied-to-hezbollah-who-was-hamas-official-saleh-al-arouri/0000018c-cbb3-d4e1-ad8f-ffb31c580000</link><description>周二晚上，阿鲁里在贝鲁特南部被杀，他是哈马斯政治派别中一位有影响力和魅力的领导人。他是多起针对以色列的恐怖袭击的幕后黑手，并参与了人质交换谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/coordinated-with-sinwar-tied-to-hezbollah-who-was-hamas-official-saleh-al-arouri/0000018c-cbb3-d4e1-ad8f-ffb31c580000</guid></item><item><title>一定是艾伦·德肖维茨为以色列辩护，反对种族灭绝指控吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-02/ty-article/.highlight/alan-dershowitz-cant-be-israels-only-option-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-cae3-d4e1-ad8f-fef3a20e0000</link><description>为什么以色列必须求助于德肖维茨——多年来他已被证明是从事“德肖维茨生意”的——而不是一个真正具有国际法诚意的人？</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 18:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-02/ty-article/.highlight/alan-dershowitz-cant-be-israels-only-option-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-cae3-d4e1-ad8f-fef3a20e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名周二在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-north-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018c-cb16-d4e1-ad8f-ffb776490000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，在导致参谋军士死亡的事件中，另有三人受重伤。苏菲安·达加什 (Sufian Dagash)，曾在工程兵部队服役</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 17:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-north-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018c-cb16-d4e1-ad8f-ffb776490000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯确认最高领导人萨拉赫·阿鲁里在贝鲁特爆炸中丧生；指责以色列暗杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/hamas-confirms-top-leader-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut-blames-israel-for-assassination/0000018c-cb0a-d4e1-ad8f-ffbb95e30000</link><description>阿鲁里是哈马斯政治局副局长，仅次于伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚。黎巴嫩报道称爆炸是由以色列无人机袭击造成的</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 17:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/hamas-confirms-top-leader-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut-blames-israel-for-assassination/0000018c-cb0a-d4e1-ad8f-ffbb95e30000</guid></item><item><title>那个被称为傀儡但自比为希律王的人又回到了以色列外交部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/king-herod-or-netanyahus-puppet-yisrael-katz-is-back-in-israels-foreign-ministry/0000018c-c5f5-d6c4-ab8d-e5f58e010000</link><description>外交部长伊斯雷尔·卡茨与伊莱·科恩交换职位，回到了被剥夺了大部分权力和声望的工作岗位，但他着眼于更大的奖品：当本杰明·内塔尼亚胡退出政治舞台时</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 16:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/king-herod-or-netanyahus-puppet-yisrael-katz-is-back-in-israels-foreign-ministry/0000018c-c5f5-d6c4-ab8d-e5f58e010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将任命法官并为国际法院加沙种族灭绝听证会准备辩护团队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-appoint-judge-prepare-defense-team-for-icj-hearing-on-gaza-genocide/0000018c-ca94-ddba-abad-cab56ecf0000</link><description>以色列正在组建一个部际小组，准备对南非提交的请愿书进行辩护。以色列人权专家指责以色列执法人员没有对以色列政客呼吁种族清洗和种族灭绝的极端言论采取行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 16:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-appoint-judge-prepare-defense-team-for-icj-hearing-on-gaza-genocide/0000018c-ca94-ddba-abad-cab56ecf0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查发现，75％的犹太以色列人拒绝美国将加沙战争转移到新阶段的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/75-of-jewish-israelis-reject-u-s-demand-to-shift-gaza-war-to-new-phase-poll-finds/0000018c-caa4-d4e1-ad8f-feb5bdda0000</link><description>56%的阿拉伯受访者表示以色列应该屈服于美国的压力，大多数左翼犹太人也同意战争应该转向精确瞄准哈马斯领导人</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 15:19:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/75-of-jewish-israelis-reject-u-s-demand-to-shift-gaza-war-to-new-phase-poll-finds/0000018c-caa4-d4e1-ad8f-feb5bdda0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼议员威胁：“我们将与哈马斯、真主党打交道，然后是最高法院”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/far-right-lawmaker-threatens-we-will-deal-with-hamas-hezbollah-then-the-supreme-court/0000018c-caa6-d4e1-ad8f-feb71d610000</link><description>高等法院周一否决了一项重要的司法政变法后，来自 Ben-Gvir 领导的 Otzma Yehudit 党的 MK Tzvika Foghel 在 X 上发布了这一威胁。战时内阁成员甘茨称这种比较“卑鄙可耻”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 15:16:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/far-right-lawmaker-threatens-we-will-deal-with-hamas-hezbollah-then-the-supreme-court/0000018c-caa6-d4e1-ad8f-feb71d610000</guid></item></channel></rss>